#ROOM
Vnum     29000
Name     &rThe Kraul Entrance&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive wall of thorns and briars twists together to form the 
entrance to the Kraul. The air is thick with the smell of wet earth 
and the musk of quilboar. A swirling, blood-red portal hums with 
magical energy, separating the thorny tunnels from the Barrens 
outside.
~
#EXIT
Direction out~
ToRoom    26532
Desc      Return to the Barrens.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29001
Desc      The path leads into the thorns.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29001
Name     &rOuter Thorns - Path Entry&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls of this tunnel are made of living, pulsating vines. 
Sharp thorns protrude from every surface, making any movement 
hazardous. The sound of distant snorting and the clatter of bone 
echoes through the passage.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29000
Desc      The entrance portal.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29002
Desc      The path continues deeper.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29001 10 29001
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29002
Name     &rOuter Thorns - Narrow Bend&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The tunnel turns sharply here. Deep gouges in the rock floor 
suggest the frequent passage of heavy kodo or boar beasts. The 
vines here are thicker, almost choking the path.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29001
Desc      The entry path.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    29003
Desc      A small side cavern.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29004
Desc      The path toward the crossroads.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29002 10 29002
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29003
Name     &rThorny Side Cavern&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This small alcove is used as a temporary storage area. Piles of 
discarded bone and crude wooden staves are stacked against the 
twisting walls.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    29002
Desc      Return to the path.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29011 10 29003
Reset O 0 29038 10 29003
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29004
Name     &rOuter Thorns - Approaching the Hub&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air is heavy with the scent of ozone. Strange, glowing 
totems have been planted along the walls, casting a flickering, 
blue light upon the jagged briars.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29002
Desc      The narrow bend.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29005
Desc      The central crossroads.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29000 10 29004
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29005
Name     &rRoalgorth's Crossroads&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This wide, circular chamber serves as the primary hub of the 
lower Kraul. Tunnels branch off in all directions, guarded by 
the elite warriors of the Razorfen tribe. A massive, blood-stained 
altar sits in the center.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29004
Desc      The outer thorns.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29011
Desc      The path to Overlord Ramtusk.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    29006
Desc      The path to Death Speaker Jargba.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    29016
Desc      The path to Agathelos.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29015 1 29005
  Reset E 1 29026 1 14
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29006
Name     &dDeath's Head Passage - Entry&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The natural briars here have been draped in dark, tattered 
banners. The atmosphere is chilling, and the sound of 
monotonous chanting vibrates through the floor.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    29005
Desc      The crossroads.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    29007
Desc      The passage continues.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29012 10 29006
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29007
Name     &dDeath's Head Passage - Acolyte Hall&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Shadowy figures move through the gloom here. The walls are 
covered in necromantic symbols painted in ash. Several small 
braziers burn with a cold, purple flame.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    29006
Desc      The passage entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29008
Desc      A small ritual room.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29009
Desc      A small ritual room.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    29010
Desc      The inner sanctum entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29012 10 29007
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29008
Name     &dRitual Room of Bones&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Piles of quilboar skulls are arranged in neat circles on the 
floor. It appears the Death's Head acolytes are using this 
space to harvest energy from the deceased.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29007
Desc      The acolyte hall.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29013 10 29008
Reset O 0 29033 1 29008
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29009
Name     &dRitual Room of Shadows&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The air is thick with a magical fog that obscures your vision. 
Ghostly whispers echo off the walls, speaking in a tongue 
that sounds like grinding stone.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29007
Desc      The acolyte hall.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29013 10 29009
Reset O 0 29039 10 29009
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29010
Name     &dDeath Speaker's Threshold&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A heavy gate made of sharpened bones blocks the path forward. 
The scent of rot is overwhelming here, and the light from the 
braziers is almost extinguished by the darkness beyond.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    29007
Desc      The acolyte hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29011
Desc      The Death Speaker's Chamber.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29004 10 29010
