#ROOM
Vnum     29011
Name     &dDeath Speaker Jargba's Chamber&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This large, vaulted chamber is the heart of the Death's Head 
operations. Jargba stands before a massive, pulsating pile of 
corrupted thorns, conducting a ritual that bleeds the very 
life from the earth.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29010
Desc      The threshold.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29016 1 29011
  Reset E 1 29024 1 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29012
Name     &WThe High Road - North&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This path climbs steeply away from the crossroads. The tunnels 
here are wider and better maintained, indicating this is the 
way to the tribe's military leadership.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29005
Desc      The crossroads.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29013
Desc      The military corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29001 10 29012
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29013
Name     &WThe Military Corridor&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Iron-capped pillars support the ceiling here. Quilboar guards 
patrol this hallway with disciplined precision, their armor 
clanking with every step.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29012
Desc      The north path.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29014
Desc      The Overlord's approach.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29005 10 29013
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29014
Name     &WThe Overlord's Approach&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls are lined with captured banners from various Horde and 
Alliance outposts. This hallway serves as a grim trophy room 
for the Overlord's many victories.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29013
Desc      The military corridor.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    29015
Desc      Overlord Ramtusk's Seat.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29009 10 29014
Reset O 0 29030 5 29014
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29015
Name     &WOverlord Ramtusk's Seat&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive throne carved from the skull of a kodo dominates the 
far wall. Overlord Ramtusk sits here, surrounded by his most 
loyal advisors, planning the next strike against the Barrens.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    29014
Desc      The approach.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29017 1 29015
  Reset E 1 29025 1 6
  Reset G 1 29034 1
