#ROOM
Vnum     29016
Name     &gThe Great Boar's Path - West&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The stone here is replaced by thick, spongy moss. The tunnels 
smell of fresh water and ancient forest. This wing is the 
spiritual home of the tribe's beastmasters.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    29005
Desc      The crossroads.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    29017
Desc      The beastmaster's walk.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29007 10 29016
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29017
Name     &gThe Beastmaster's Walk&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Small pens have been carved into the rock here, housing the 
snarling hyenas and boars used by the tribe. The sounds of 
barking and snapping jaws fill the air.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    29016
Desc      The western path.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29018
Desc      A small beast pen.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29019
Desc      A small beast pen.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    29020
Desc      The descent to the lair.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29008 10 29017
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29018
Name     &gBeast Pen - North&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The floor is covered in shredded leather and half-eaten kodo 
meat. It is a violent and messy place, even by quilboar 
standards.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29017
Desc      The walk.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29008 10 29018
Reset O 0 29036 5 29018
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29019
Name     &gBeast Pen - South&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls here are covered in deep scratch marks. It seems 
the inhabitants of this pen were particularly restless.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29017
Desc      The walk.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29008 10 29019
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29020
Name     &gThe Descent to the Lair&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The tunnel slopes steeply downward into a massive, natural 
cavern. The air is warm and smells of damp fur. A low, rhythmic 
