~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    29017
Desc      The walk.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    29021
Desc      Agathelos's Lair.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29007 10 29020
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29021
Name     &gAgathelos's Lair&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This immense cavern is the resting place of Agathelos the 
Raging. The floor is soft sand, and the walls are draped in 
flowering briars that glow with a soft, green light. The great 
boar spirit stands in the center, a primal force of nature.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    29020
Desc      Return to the path.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29018 1 29021
  Reset G 1 29020 1
  Reset G 1 29022 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29022
Name     &MThe Path to the Crone - entry&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This path is the most heavily fortified in the Kraul. Massive 
thorns are braided into impenetrable walls, leaving only a 
narrow, winding path through the center.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29005
Desc      The crossroads.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29023
Desc      The inner path.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 29006 10 29022
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     29023
Name     &MThe Inner Path&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Magical energy crackles through the air here. Small sparks of 
