#ROOM
Vnum     29024
Name     &MThe Final Ascent&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The path climbs toward a high, sunlit opening in the cavern 
roof. The sound of a cackling laugh echoes down the tunnel, 
marking the location of Charlga Razorflank.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29023
Desc      The inner path.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29025
