the seat of power for the entire Razorfen tribe.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29024
Desc      The ascent.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    29026
Desc      Charlga Razorflank's Seat.~
