#ROOM
Vnum     29026
Name     &MCharlga Razorflank's Seat&d~
Sector   underground~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Charlga Razorflank stands on a high stone platform, overlooking 
her tribe. She is surrounded by jars of strange fluids and 
piles of ancient, dusty scrolls. Her eyes glow with a 
calculated, dangerous intelligence.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    29025
Desc      The entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
